### Variables
@baseUrl = https://festive-guest-api.azurewebsites.net
@userId = test-user-id
@adminToken = your-admin-jwt-token-here

### Get Subscription Status
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/subscription/{{userId}}

### Get All Users with Subscriptions (Admin Only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/subscription/admin/all
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Update Subscription (Admin Only) - Set to Pending
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/subscription/update
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "{{userId}}",
  "subscriptionStatus": "pending",
  "paymentVerifiedTimestamp": null
}

### Update Subscription (Admin Only) - Set to Paid
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/subscription/update
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "{{userId}}",
  "subscriptionStatus": "paid",
  "paymentVerifiedTimestamp": "2024-01-15T10:30:00Z"
}

### Update Subscription (Admin Only) - Set to Free
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/subscription/update
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "{{userId}}",
  "subscriptionStatus": "free",
  "paymentVerifiedTimestamp": null
}
